This Snapshot Has Been Released In Sunday March 8 2026 New Feature Added
1 Added The Wiki On /etc/os-release add DOCUMENTATION_URL=https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux/wiki
  Run sudo nano /etc/os-release
  then add DOCUMENTATION_URL=https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux/wiki after the HOME_URL
  Example
  BUILD_ID=rolling
  HOME_URL="https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux"
  DOCUMENTATION_URL=https://github.com/Haikal02-alt/Triaxis-GNU-Linux/wiki
  
2 Added Wayland For KDE Plasma And Set To Default You Can Add It Using This Command
  sudo apt update
  sudo apt install plasma-workspace-wayland
  sudo reboot
